{"tid":1789741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"trump彈劾關香港事","createTime":"2019-12-19T13:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T14:22:56.000Z","uid":324569,"like":30,"dislike":117,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"91eab34183bcddd9b316d3897651e741596471f7","tid":1789741,"uid":324569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:22:48.000Z","msg":"留意以下截圖嘅日期：<br />\n9月18日Nancy Pelosi接見黃之鋒，高調推動香港人權法。<br />\n9月20日，事隔兩日，相信係喺中共強大嘅反對壓力下，使出各種收買賤招，Nancy Pelosi搵咗一個無厘頭嘅原因，話要開始彈劾Donald Trump。隨即，本來應承急速推動香港人權法，突然間全美國全世界嘅注意力同焦點，都轉風向去彈劾美國總統到，於是香港人權法被擺埋一二邊個幾兩個月，呢一段時間亦都係香港最黑暗嘅10月。<br />\n如果唔係彈劾總統，香港人權法喺10月初都過左啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tnudHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tnudHJ.jpg&h=2e46b844&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LmCnA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LmCnA4.jpg&h=891e4b74&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jr2xVV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJr2xVV5.jpg&h=d804d8ba&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1O85wur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1O85wur.jpg&h=f2567cb6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再睇下9月24日， Donald Trump喺聯合國百幾個國家領袖面前講話支持香港抗爭，否定共產黨社會主義。點知同一日，Nancy Pelosi正式宣佈啟動總統彈劾程序⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n時間上咁吻合，唔係中共做都無人信！中共驚住香港人權法通過，出盡全力喺美國干擾，出到呢一招。"},{"pid":"4e3126718388b0964e586a41a0581d2cbaaa4460","tid":1789741,"uid":126283,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:24:55.000Z","msg":"但係已經立左啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6dccd6ea28856ee43262964ea239ad6e73a0d3","tid":1789741,"uid":35364,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"關香港春事咩，關心香港就研究匯豐啦"},{"pid":"d4ba58b77ce0328585aee75c7ee981226ac26742","tid":1789741,"uid":146285,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:2